Necros could chain pets with thier root, if they needed to. The reason they don't chain is simply because they have better options, not because of anything to do with thier pets. Same thing with any other pet class, but even more so. Only beastlords are unable to chain pets, but with thier superior pet heals, and still very nice pets they are at less mob mercy than we are. Besides, they do get sow in the 40's I believe, which often would be all they need to survive most situations.<br>
